task.summary: First Working Version - supports File Upload - resume Conversion via LiveDocx - Supports OpenId Login - still needs actual security

Customize the Login page + friendly URL + alternate URLs for completeness/ease of use + buttons for google/yahoo + Added BonBon Button CSS to make the buttons look nice. Locked down the Admin page to Admins only Updated OpenIdUser and OpenIdUserManager to get the known admin emails from parameters.yml Corrected the debugging User display on the index page removed the Symfony form code from navBar in favor of a plain html form.(button)
Added a git ingore file to ensure uploaded resumes dureing testing don't get accidentally added to the repository
Add a readme.md file to the project with a brief description
readme.md - updated with link for PHPLiveDocX removed Unnecessary default files. Added Necessary config files. Added Base html template
Added bootstrap.php.cache - necessary symfony config class updated .gitignore to allow it.
Logging updated/File Controller fixed - logging output is caught by the Cloudbees System - FileController now correctly grabs property resume.FolderLocation
Controller corrections to do the variable dumping in the control and only display the output on the page.
